Package: slic4d
Type: Package
Title: Fast 4D SLIC Supervoxels for Neuroimaging (mask-aware, gradient relocation, preserve-K)
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com")
Description: A fast SLIC-style supervoxel algorithm for 4D neuroimaging volumes (x,y,z,time), with mask-aware seeding (maskSLIC-style), strict connectivity, gradient-based seed relocation, and an option to preserve exactly K labels.
